  "title": "Calming upset customers staying effective during unpleasant situations",
  "abstract": "Rebecca L. Morgan, CSP, CMC, is a people-productivity expert. She travels interna-tionally to share her research and experience to help make people and organizations more productive and profitable. Her areas of expertise include sales, time management, communication, and creating customer service excellence. Coverage includes- To explain the psychology that governs upset customer behavior To suggest procedures to take after the customer is gone To present strategies for successful customer encounters To advise managers about actions and attitudes",
